---
title: Creamy Potato, Leek & Feta Filo Pie with Cucumber & Almond Salad
description: Golden, crispy and oh-so-creamy! This filo pie wraps up the comforting flavours of potato and leek in delicate, flaky layers, with
a hint of tangy feta in every bite. A fresh, crunchy salad is all you need to round out this superstar meal!
